Package com.cyc.km.query.export Description

Provides the classes specific to exporting Cyc queries. In general, exporting query results involves the following steps:
  1. creating and running a Query
  2. instantiating a subclass of ResultsExporter
  3. calling the appropriate export method
Reference implementations are provided for comma-separated values (com.cyc.km.query.export.CSVResultsExporter) and XML (com.cyc.km.query.export.CycXMLQueryResultExporter).
